io.lettuce.core

Class KeyValue<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.lettuce.core.Value<V>
      • io.lettuce.core.KeyValue<K,V>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - Key type.
    V - Value type.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class KeyValue<K,V>
extends Value<V>
    A key-value container extension to Value. A KeyValue requires always a non-null key on construction.
    Author:
    Will Glozer, Mark Paluch
    See Also:
